    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1886-10-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1886-10-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="409" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d409">
                <head>No. 404.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Curry</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1886-10-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 20, 1886</date>.
                            (Received October 20—9 p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Curry informs Mr. Bayard that he has been desired by the Spanish minister
                        of state to say that the statement is authorized by the Government of Spain
                        that it much desires the arrangement of the disagreement with the Government
                        of the United States.</p>
            </div>
